column21: Wellcome Global Monitor Trust in Scientists Index (recoded into 3 categories) High Trust
column22: Q11E How much do you trust each of the following? How about doctors and nurses in this country? Do you trust them a lot, some, not much, or not at all? A lot
column23: Q11B How much do you trust each of the following? How about the national government in this country? Do you trust them a lot, some, not much, or not at all? A lot
